Class ArtistCorrelator

  • Object
    • ArtistCorrelator

  • public class ArtistCorrelator
extends Object
    Class that represents a correlator between the ArtistNames object (which contains various forms of an artist name), and the corresponding Artist object (which contains all other artist data). This class contains the key for the map that houses all the Artist objects.
    Author:
    Jon
